OL,3,CChief Constable to carry out 'internal
OL,4,Creview' into Isle of Man incident
OL,6,FThe Chief Constable of the Isle of Man
OL,7,Fis carrying out an 'internal review'
OL,8,Finto the Constabulary's handling of
OL,9,Fthe serious incident in Maughold.
OL,11,FIt comes after a public meeting, where
OL,12,Fresidents shared concerns over the
OL,13,Fpolice response to a 'serious
OL,14,Fincident' on Cornaa beach.
OL,16,FTwo people were left injured,
OL,17,Fincluding a man who was flown to
OL,18,FAintree Hospital for treatment.
