OL,3,CChief Constable to carry out 'internal
OL,4,Creview' into Isle of Man incident
OL,6,FIn a statement, the minister for Home
OL,7,FAffairs, Jane Poole-Wilson said: 'The
OL,8,FDepartment of Home Affairs is aware
OL,9,Fthat the recent serious incident in
OL,10,FMaughold has caused some public
OL,11,Fconcern about the Police's handling of
OL,12,Fthe incident and the public
OL,13,Fcommunication during the ongoing
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,F'The Chief Constable is currently
OL,17,Fcarrying out an internal review of the
OL,18,Fway in which the incident was dealt
OL,19,Fwith and also how information was used
OL,20,Fand disseminated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
