OL,3,CChief Constable to carry out 'internal
OL,4,Creview' into Isle of Man incident
OL,6,F'I am keen to ensure that his review
OL,7,Fis completed and the first stage of
OL,8,Fthe Police investigation is complete `
OL,9,Fincluding the laying of any charges `
OL,10,Fbefore determining what steps, if any,
OL,11,Fare to be taken next.
OL,13,F'I am also aware that other agencies
OL,14,Fhave been involved in this matter and
OL,15,Fso we need to understand their role in
OL,16,Fthis too.'
OL,18,FBoth the Isle of Man Constabulary and
OL,19,Fthe Isle of Man Government have been
OL,20,Fapproached for interviews.
